<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Rewards Dashboard</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f6f8;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 30px 16px;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .card h4 {
      margin: 14px 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }

    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin: 14px 0;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      background: #eef2ff;
      color: #3730a3;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- SECTION 1 -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>🎁 Monthly Raffle</h2>

      <div class="card">

        <div class="badge">Monthly Program</div>

        <p>
          Any child with 90% participation will be entered into our monthly raffle.
          The raffle is held on the last day of every month.
        </p>

        <hr>

        <h4>🏆 February Winners</h4>

        <p>
          <b>$10 Gift Cards:</b><br>
          Ava S. • Liam K. • Noah R. • Emma T. • Sophia B.
        </p>

        <p>
          <b>$50 Gift Cards:</b><br>
          Chaim A. • Jordan B. • Madison C.
        </p>

        <p>
          <b>Board Games:</b><br>
          Sima A. • Noah B. • Ava C.
        </p>

        <p>
          <b>LEGO:</b><br>
          Ethan A. • Sophia B. • Benjamin C.
        </p>

        <p>
          <b>Tickets:</b><br>
          Chava A. • Mason B. • Emily C.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SECTION 2 -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>🎉 Participation Rewards</h2>

      <div class="card">

        <p>
          Keep up the good work, kids — to date, we’ve given away thousands of dollars in rewards.
        </p>

        <p>
          Anyone who has just started following their guidelines may ask their Hospital of CARE provider
          to apply for the $50 beginner’s bonus.
        </p>

        <p>
          Please ensure that all paperwork is submitted in a timely manner.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
